  "2026-06-30T08:14:13.517Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: implemented PR #406 reviewer follow-up by adding resetActiveExtensionRegistries() in src/mcp/server.ts and invoking it immediately in the activation catch path before fallback run(active=null), with final teardown using the same reset helper. Added regression coverage in tests/unit/mcp/mcp-server-branch-residual.spec.ts that simulates a setActiveExtensionCommands publish failure and asserts fallback stats execution only happens after hooks/commands/parsers/preflight/services/renderers/registrations have all been reset to empty registries. Focused linked test passed. Broader gates passed: pnpm build; pnpm lint including static quality gate; pnpm typecheck; pnpm contracts:check; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage = 262 files / 5258 tests / 100% statements, branches, functions, lines; pnpm changelog:pm:check using pm-changelog 2026.6.30 with CHANGELOG.md unchanged; pnpm security:scan no credential-like secrets; pnpm audit --audit-level moderate no known vulnerabilities; manual temp-dir smoke passed after correcting init syntax (init/create/list/install pm-changelog/package doctor/changelog generate); Sentry CLI returned recent PM-CLI issue data; sentry-telemetry gate passed with zero critical/high blocking Sentry issues and telemetry finish_error_rate_pct 0.78."
  "2026-06-30T08:15:08.674Z",claude-code-agent,"GitHub/release-health evidence: gh issue list shows only open issue #374 (Auto Release blocked: scheduled run failed). gh issue view #374 and gh run view 28425418015 show the current June 30 scheduled Auto Release failed in the Run auto release pipeline step because release_pat_configured=false while sentry_personal_admin_token_configured=true. Latest five Auto Release workflow runs are all scheduled main failures for the same missing RELEASE_PAT protected-main publish path. This is existing release-environment configuration debt, not a code regression from PR #406; canonical pm item is pm-7zs0, so no duplicate pm item was created."
  "2026-06-30T08:25:19.574Z",claude-code-agent,"Greptile pre-push review evidence: greptile review show f1fdb0fe-76e8-42ba-9b9e-542fa38ee9e3 completed on committed head 3513e8a5 with Confidence 4/5, Safe to merge, and 'No review comments.'"
  "2026-06-30T08:35:02.014Z",claude-code-agent,"Review-loop follow-up: accepted CodeRabbit feedback on PR #406 by restoring console.error spies in finally blocks and asserting deactivateExtensions runs after the simulated partial registry publish failure. Validation: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/mcp/mcp-server-branch-residual.spec.ts; pnpm lint; pnpm typecheck; git diff --check all pass."
